{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5332b68cbc","title":"关于大学教育改革的一段谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"686df9c4e9","index":0,"year":1968,"month":7,"day":12,"articleId":"5332b68cbc"}],"tags":[{"id":"299424f798","name":"教育和教育革命","type":"主题"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"06f8834dab","type":"title","text":"关于大学教育改革的一段谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5332b68cbc"},{"id":"24876a0ef1","type":"paragraph","text":"大学还是要办的，我这里主要说的是理工科大学还要办，但学制要缩短，教育要革命，要无产阶级政治挂帅，走上海机床厂从工人中培养技术人员的道路。要从有实践经验的工人农民中间选拔学生，到学校学几年以后，又回到生产实践中去。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5332b68cbc"}],"page":{"id":"fdf45dba30","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5332b68cbc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}